@page "/staff-rules"
<PageTitle>Staff Rules - SentrySMP</PageTitle>

Remember you’re here to keep the server safe and enjoyable. Teamwork makes everything smoother. 😊
<h3>Respect All Members</h3>
Treat every player fairly, regardless of rank. No favoritism or discrimination.
 
<h3>Be Professional</h3>
Avoid toxic behavior, arguments, or abuse of staff powers. You represent the server.

<h3>No Abuse of Permissions</h3>
Do not use staff commands (fly, tp, ban, kick, mute, etc.) for personal gain or jokes.

<h3>Stay Active & Available</h3>
Try to be online regularly. If you’ll be inactive, inform the team.

<h3>Enforce Rules Consistently</h3>
All punishments must follow the server’s punishment guidelines.

<h3>No Staff Drama in Public</h3>
Keep disagreements within staff channels. Don’t argue in front of players.

<h3>Confidentiality</h3>
Staff discussions, plans, and reports must stay in staff-only areas.

<h3>Use Common Sense</h3>
If something isn’t written in the rules but feels wrong, don’t do it.

<h3>Report Issues Promptly</h3>
If you see bugs, exploits, or player issues you can’t solve, report them to higher staff.

<h3>Be Helpful & Approachable</h3>
Assist players kindly. Don’t ignore questions or requests for help.

<h3>No Staff Privilege in Gameplay</h3>
Play the game fairly. Don’t spawn items, cheat, or give yourself unfair advantages.

<h3>Have Fun & Work as a Team. </h3>

<p>Just enjoy playing!</p>

<h3>Staff isn't allowed to raid bases. </h3>

<p>Under <b>no</b> circumstances may you destroy other players' buildings.</p>

<p>Effective Date: November 21, 2025</p>